name: Hackerbreakfast
body:
### Welcome to Hacker Breakfast! Hacker Breakfast is a weekly meeting of local people interested in all things technology. Bring your laptop and come work on personal projects, bounce ideas off of people, and get to know fellow nerds in the area. ### Schedule We meet every Sunday at 10:00am. Most people stick around for a couple of hours, but there is no schedule. Swing by any time! ### Location We meet at [Revel77 Coffee](http://www.revel77coffee.com/) on the South Hill... ``` 3223 E 57TH AVE STE K SPOKANE WA 99223-6010 ```
View Larger Map [Directions to Revel77](https://maps.google.com/maps?daddr=Revel+77+Coffee,+3223+East+57th+Avenue,+Spokane,+WA+99223&hl=en&sll=47.594774,-117.392151&sspn=0.046537,0.068665&geocode=FWNa1gIdVi4B-SlvshVKBiOeVDEbMrqqPEmfCQ&mra=ls&t=m&z=14)
